    • Constructor Detail

      • Monster

        public Monster(MonsterType monsterType,
               Path path)
        Links a monster type to a given path on the board to create a monster to attack the player. The constructor initiates all of the required variables for both attacking, death and traversal.
        Parameters:
        monsterType - the characters of the new monster.
        path - the path upon which the new monster will travel.

        public void move(float remainingMovement)
